gularized frozen star and discuss its\n$\\varepsilon\\to 0$ limit, for which the geometry degenerates and becomes\neffectively two dimensional.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2023 20:37:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
