a and speed to train the neural model present it\nas an encouraging competitor in earthquake forecasting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 12:15:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 09:45:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-12"}
