 in intergalactic scales, we find a lower bound on the PBH\nmass within the range $[10^{10}- 10^{16}]M_\\odot$ depending on the radius of\nthe PBH disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 14:39:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 14:31:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
